r />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制「邪惡」「無良」的商戶，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n2. 安全之下，免費港鐵；二人同遊，一人免費<br />\n3. 夜晚十點吶喊！！！連繫左鄰右里<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests <br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=8Se%2B9W40ah4Gl3auq3G%2BukXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=966b872b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n6. 保持獨立思考，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour ，五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 低消費，高儲蓄；罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 做孝子救港，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股，MPF都買美股<br />\n2. 搵多一個人參與<br />\n3. 關心社會事務，做陪審員啦<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.09"},{"pid":"cb2dfce276bb97b14add9a60d70d06f9edcc2aad","tid":1555080,"uid":283541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b85306fac94298b45ae64a2c9296bd7a5bee62c7","tid":1555080,"uid":173002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"229d9efb95575410707349530c46c65927ec48d6","tid":1555080,"uid":201374,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"ece762e5daa5473a5b645bc2030660a5f1bb8861","tid":1555080,"uid":31173,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:35:29.000Z","msg":"反而堵路，放火，破壞港鐵個d走晒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:41:33.000Z","msg":"老實講，實際行動嘅一定有晒策略點行點走<br />\n拉唔到好正常"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:42:39.000Z","msg":"最大問題係街坊，同趁熱鬧嘅行人。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:26:18.000Z","msg":"應該告唔入？"},{"pid":"18954b964c647fa6617c0324022241076a533ed6","tid":1555080,"uid":282435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"918279e4492ebc9a91b0a8e8e7b2395eeb681cb7","tid":1555080,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy